
Disadvantages.        
Online LearningPros:
Flexibility: Learners can study at their own pace and on their own schedule, fitting education into busy lives. 
Accessibility: Access to a wide range of courses and instructors from around the world, without geographic limitations. 
Cost-Effective: Can be cheaper due to reduced travel, accommodation, and physical infrastructure costs. 
Personalization: Allows students to focus more time on challenging concepts, leading to deeper understanding.
